			<p><b>Nagato Operational Timeline</b></p><table border='0' cellspacing='0'><tr bgcolor='eeeeee'><td valign='top' align='right' nowrap><a href='/event/today/11/15/1920' alt='See all events on 15 Nov 1920' title='See all events on 15 Nov 1920' class='noStyle'>15 Nov 1920</a>&nbsp;</td><td>Nagato was commissioned into service.</td></tr><tr bgcolor=''><td valign='top' align='right' nowrap><a href='/event/today/07/14/1942' alt='See all events on 14 Jul 1942' title='See all events on 14 Jul 1942' class='noStyle'>14 Jul 1942</a>&nbsp;</td><td>Nagato was transferred to Combined Fleet Battleship Division 2.</td></tr><tr bgcolor='eeeeee'><td valign='top' align='right' nowrap><a href='/event/today/07/18/1945' alt='See all events on 18 Jul 1945' title='See all events on 18 Jul 1945' class='noStyle'>18 Jul 1945</a>&nbsp;</td><td>Nagato was damaged in port at Yokosuka, Japan during an American carrier air raid.  A destroyer, a sumarine, and three smaller vessels were sunk during the attack.</td></tr></table><br /><p><b>Photographs</b></p><table cellpadding='2' cellspacing='0' border='0'><tr><td><a href='/photo.php?source=all&color=all&list=search&foreigntype=S&foreigntype_id=26'><img src="/images/imagemagick/tmb_ship_nagato4.jpg" border='0' alt='Battleship Nagato, circa early 1920s'></a></td><td><a href='/photo.php?source=all&color=all&list=search&foreigntype=S&foreigntype_id=26'><img src="/images/imagemagick/tmb_ship_tatsuta7.jpg" border='0' alt='Nagato, Mutsu, and Tatsuta, 1927'></a></td><td><a href='/photo.php?source=all&color=all&list=search&foreigntype=S&foreigntype_id=26'><img src="/images/imagemagick/tmb_ship_akagi8.jpg" border='0' alt='Carrier Akagi and battleship Nagato at Yokosuka Naval Arsenal, Japan, 15 Aug 1927'></a></td><td><a href='/photo.php?source=all&color=all&list=search&foreigntype=S&foreigntype_id=26'><img src="/images/imagemagick/tmb_ship_fuso5.jpg" border='0' alt='Japanese battleships Fuso (foreground), Nagato (center), and Mutsu (background) at Mitajiri, Japan, 1928'></a></td></tr></table><a href='/photo.php?source=all&color=all&list=search&foreigntype=S&foreigntype_id=26'>See all 23 photographs of Battleship Nagato</a><br /><p><b>Videos</b></p><table cellpadding='2' cellspacing='0' border='0'><tr><td><a href="/video/28"><img src='http://img.youtube.com/vi/appnmHdGLSk/mqdefault.jpg' width='150' border='0' alt='Battleship Nagato, post war'></a></td></tr></table><br /><br /><br /><br />
